<p>Practical first-month implementation plan for a typical restaurant.</p>
<h3>Week 1: Audit Current State</h3>
<p>Document current Google Business Profile, Apple Business Connect, Yelp, and major OTA listings. Take baseline metrics: average rating, review velocity, GBP impressions, current marketing time investment.</p>
